---

const ctaLink = "#";
const demoLink = "#";
---

<section>
  <div class="mx-auto w-full lg:px-24 max-w-7xl md:px-12 items-center px-8 py-24">
    <div class="text-center max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <p class="text-4xl tracking-tight font-semibold md:text-5xl font-display mt-8">
        Spoke: Peer-to-Peer Texting Made Simple
      </p>
      <p class="lg:text-xl max-w-2xl mt-4 mx-auto text-base">
        Built by experts from the Bernie 2020 campaign, Spoke is the most cost-effective tool to mobilize your base quickly, engage effectively, and scale your outreach efforts seamlessly.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="flex justify-center gap-3 mt-10 flex-col sm:flex-row">
      <a
        class="items-center no-underline justify-center border-gray-200 h-12 font-medium rounded-xl focus-visible:outline-black focus:outline-none inline-flex duration-200 lg:w-auto px-6 py-3 text-center w-full border"
        href={ctaLink}>View Pricing</a>
      <a
        class="items-center no-underline justify-center h-12 font-medium rounded-xl focus-visible:outline-black focus:outline-none inline-flex border-2 border-black duration-200 focus-visible:ring-black lg:w-auto px-6 py-3 text-center w-full"
        href={demoLink}>Get Started &nbsp; &rarr;</a>
    </div>
    <dl class="lg:gap-x-8 lg:grid-cols-3 max-w-4xl mt-8 mx-auto sm:gap-x-6 sm:gap-y-12 sm:grid sm:grid-cols-2 sm:space-y-0 space-y-6 text-center text-sm items-start">
      <div>
        <strong>Cost-Effective Texting</strong> ━ Save on infrastructure fees, and only pay for the texts you send with no hidden costs.
      </div>
      <div>
        <strong>Seamless Integration</strong> ━ Easily sync your text campaigns with your CRM, ensuring all data is captured and tracked.
      </div>
      <div>
        <strong>Proven Performance</strong> ━ Over 1 billion texts sent and $15 million saved for campaigns and organizations.
      </div>
    </dl>
    <div class="relative w-full mx-auto max-w-7xl items-center py-12 pb-12">
      <div class="bg-gray-100 p-8 rounded-3xl">
        <img
          alt="Spoke Dashboard"
          class="relative w-full border border-gray-200 lg:rounded-2xl object-cover rounded shadow-2xl"
          src="https://brightlight.lexingtonthemes.com/assets/dashboard.svg"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-0.5 lg:mt-8 md:grid-cols-6 mt-6">
      <div class="flex justify-center col-span-1">
        <img alt="Bernie logo" class="h-8" src="/Bernie.svg" />
      </div>
      <div class="flex justify-center col-span-1">
        <img alt="350 logo" class="h-8" src="/350.svg" />
      </div>
      <div class="flex justify-center col-span-1">
        <img alt="Indivisible logo" class="h-8" src="/Indivisible.svg" />
      </div>
      <div class="flex justify-center col-span-1">
        <img alt="Power in Numbers logo" class="h-8" src="/POWER.png" />
      </div>
      <div class="flex justify-center col-span-1">
        <img alt="Winning Mark logo" class="h-8" src="/Winning.svg" />
      </div>
      <div class="flex justify-center col-span-1">
        <img alt="Fight Coporate America logo" class="h-8" src="/FCA.webp" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
